    <p class="lead-text">Traditional sectional gutters have seams every few feet — and every seam is a potential leak. Seamless gutters are fabricated in a single continuous piece, custom-cut to fit your home exactly. The result is a cleaner look, fewer leaks, and longer-lasting performance.</p>
    <p class="lead-text">All Star Contracting fabricates seamless gutters on-site with our roll-forming equipment, so every measurement is precise and every installation is built specifically for your home. No shortcuts. No gaps.</p>
